{"tid":1084138,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[用完即棄] 高鐵200外判工遭解僱　60人西九龍站靜坐抗議","createTime":"2019-03-30T07:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T07:07:58.000Z","uid":51620,"like":14,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"0362044168fe338e190f94aa8ac102979bd33e30","tid":1084138,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"高鐵西九龍站日前接連發生職員於站內危站及墮軌事件，有職員直指與「被解僱」有關，每日都有職員收到解除僱傭通知，僱主卻無任何合理解釋。香港鐵路工會聯合會指，由上周四(21日)至今，已有近200人收到解僱信。約60名職員今日(30日)下午2時半在西九龍站B1大堂發起靜坐抗議，不滿港鐵「用完即棄」，要求運房局介入事件，外判承辦商國際永勝其後表示願意與工友代表對話。<br />\n<br />\n工會認為，港鐵有道德責任正視事件，斥港鐵突然指示承辦商解僱員工的行為嚴重不當，直接影響高鐵服務，要求港鐵責成國際永勝立即停止解僱，撤回已發出的解僱通知，否則不排除發起工業行動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190330/photo/bkn-20190330141641284-0330_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190330151142\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190330%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190330141641284-0330_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190330151142&h=9537efa9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8861966609a4d097f0f21839acd7f28cfcabab7f","tid":1084138,"uid":35014,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T07:25:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ed46b1d3b0979b7c5895d081f92128e89848aab","tid":1084138,"uid":13914,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"外判員工唔係用完就即棄咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53472435469317fcfc2922977c5dcbe142890884","tid":1084138,"uid":42188,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T07:27:10.000Z","msg":"靜坐俾邊個睇？<br />\n高鐵站都冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f43b7684c819a42fe106e90560f550a02fb1ece","tid":1084138,"uid":997,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T07:28:31.000Z","msg":"工業行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n外判搵過堆廢